Ruby Ki is a discord Utility bot for FFXIV Venues.

Use this link to add Ruby Ki to your discord server:
https://discord.com/oauth2/authorize?client_id=1089699861143769131&permissions=309237663744&integration_type=0&scope=bot+applications.commands

## Running Ruby Ki yourself
Run Ruby Ki via the provided docker-compose.yml file with a `.env` file and the following environment variables:

- DISCORD_TOKEN
- DISCORD_CLIENT_ID
- STORAGE_PATH

## Required Discord permissions
- Send Messages
- Send Messages in Threads
- Create Public Threads
- Embed Links